high_descs: walk over to the kitchen sink
grab a yellow cup off of the sink
place the yellow cup inside the microwave, microwave it, and take it back out
walk over to the brown wooden shelves
place the yellow cup on the top shelf of the wooden shelves
anns.task_desc: place a heated cup on top of the wooden shelves

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer left to the sink.
Pick up the cup next to the sink.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Turn around and walk straight and veer right to the shelving unit.
Place the cup on the top shelf to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup on a shelf.

high_descs: Begin walking forwards then hang a left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the kitchen counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the cup that is just below the tea kettle to the left of the sink.
Turn left and walk until you are in front of the oven, then turn right and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the cup inside then close the door and activate the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave door and remove the cup before closing the door.
Turn around over to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Place the heated cup on the top shelf of the wooden shelving unit just to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup onto the top shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
